{"tid":2056243,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"九西馮達浚: 堅反對國安法 商討細節極戇鳩","createTime":"2020-06-08T14:04:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-09T02:58:12.000Z","uid":147786,"like":39,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"28c3dc4ef4e5736f37f449c650e21db7dbcdc13d","tid":2056243,"uid":147786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T14:04:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">Link: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/404923336703619/posts/842965019566113/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F404923336703619%2Fposts%2F842965019566113%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=N73AYdKZ8ITSJgwUZ5%2B19i1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=ec82fcc8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/404923336703619/posts/842965019566113/?d=n</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">堅反對國安法 商討細節極戇鳩</span></span><br />\n<br />\n香港民意共識是徹底拒絕國安法，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">妥協及商討國安法落實細節的下場只會是作繭自縛。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n可惜，泛民老派相繼對國安法落實細節提出意見：郭榮鏗指審理國安法案件必須設立陪審團、李柱銘指應該由香港自行立法，一衆政客墮入中共的圈套，開始討論究竟國安法是否應設追溯期、在港是否應設立國安執法部門等等。<br />\n<br />\n我再次重申，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人的立場以及我個人的立場是反對任何形式的國安法立法</span></span>。縱使港共政府不斷帶風向討論落實細節，我們不用討論，亦無謂討論。無論有否追溯期、司法程序爲何，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">國安法本質已是赤裸裸剝奪香港人言論、集會、出版及新聞等各方面自由。</span></span><br />\n當美國總統爲國安法發動制裁、英國罕見跨黨反對港版國安法、美歐英日澳等八國議員爲此組建「反中共」聯盟，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人必須爭氣企硬，堅決徹底反對國安法，無須討論細節。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n中共政府必須撤回國安法；我們不能退讓，不能妥協。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">為此，香港人將抗爭到底，並已有攬炒的準備。</span></span>"},{"pid":"f8c945a737bb07d41f9b37d92834818f59162c57","tid":2056243,"uid":156099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T14:05:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9e83b05833efc9c75fcec200703286455d53f0f6","tid":2056243,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T14:06:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f876c1eee253a0b0c30a6996c05faaa3c4ca136","tid":2056243,"uid":200122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T14:10:28.000Z","msg":"推呀推呀推上熱門呀"},{"pid":"169ef6f3595d50e9d0f6ca87a04a778c691d83f7","tid":2056243,"uid":3560,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T14:10:41.000Z","msg":"終於有人講人話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢兩日啲新聞睇到我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n林鄭政府帶你spin落實細節<br />\n喺度帶頭又講追朔期陪審團<br />\n泛民班on9仔又回應佢<br />\n畀政府帶住個輿論一齊spin <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81511414a9828251309fd5b3a9a962594a9266c6","tid":2056243,"uid":184433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T14:11:27.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"273ba2d8cf371f1abeb1607db09f19b5f9491300","tid":2056243,"uid":305083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T14:12:07.000Z","msg":"真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 細乜撚野節吖, 總之成條惡法都要堅持反對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4de246ad9a8ec90baea05e2132cd75e59d85d2ff","tid":2056243,"uid":80600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T14:13:29.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5a5da4659c7062911e939f521dd8501c43a8771b","tid":2056243,"uid":227217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T14:14:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"14231a6e4f818539c68b699272b7fce68e56b142","tid":2056243,"uid":3560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T15:47:54.000Z","msg":"講真話無人推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"436afc25a681d29b2182833bd06e1dedac7b2229","tid":2056243,"uid":2665